free.util
Class BeanProperties

java.lang.Object
  free.util.BeanProperties

public class BeanProperties
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides the functionality of storing and retrieving bean properties while automatically notifying any listeners. It can be used to delegate the bean storing, retrieving and notifying work to it from the actual bean. It doesn't, however, support constrained properties. Note:This class is not thread safe.
